title: Caltex Theater [Australia Radio drama] OTR 1955
description:
Caltex Theater was an Australian show similar to the American Lux Radio Theater. It was sponsored by the Caltex Oil Company. Mostly the radio shows were adapted from top movies from the time period. The show aired from 1950 - 1959 with somewhere around 490 shows. Possibly only 7 episodes have survived.



mp3 files, 7 one hour episodes
